{"tid":237564,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)變種異煞 月黑高飛  聖誕妖怪：坎卜斯","createTime":"2017-05-10T12:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T18:30:14.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fae0f93de2921b302bb34277cd197023ed43298a","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=550cc9ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=222965c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4f127e5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d3/Gattaca_Movie_Poster_B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd3%2FGattaca_Movie_Poster_B.jpg&h=97b84f55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/af/Shawshank_Redemption_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Faf%2FShawshank_Redemption_ver2.jpg&h=15a34080&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cf/Krampus_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcf%2FKrampus_Poster.jpg&h=c4abe94e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在未來的人類世界中，有錢人可以選擇優良的基因。 文生天生帶有幾項缺陷：弱視、情緒化及短暫壽命。但是文生夢想成為太空人，為了達到心願，他假冒傑洛米進入太空公司。傑洛米因為一次意外導致癱瘓，將他的優良基因證明賣給文生。文生通過各種測試，獲得登上太空船的機會。他愛上美麗的艾琳娜，她則因為心臟病而不能執行太空任務..<br />\n<br />\n2.1947年，一位年輕的波特蘭銀行家安迪&middot;杜佛蘭（提姆&middot;羅賓斯飾）被指控殺死其妻子與其情夫，分別被判決兩個無期徒刑，進入緬因州的鯊堡監獄（蕭山克監獄）。另一方面，鯊堡監獄的交易商囚犯瑞德（摩根&middot;費里曼飾）在服刑了20年後申請假釋又被駁回，恰巧他也目睹了鯊堡監獄內新囚犯的到來，這其中也包括了安迪。新囚犯們得先與典獄長諾頓和獄警警備隊隊長海利會面，之後才會進入監獄服刑。在當晚，有一名囚犯因無法適應監獄的黑暗環境而哭喊，而後被隊長海利活活打死..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述一個不為人熟知的暗黑版聖誕節傳說,徹底顛覆我們對歡樂假期的想像。從小在衝突不斷的家庭中長大，年輕的麥斯對聖誕節早已不抱任何期望。但他一點也不知道，這種缺乏歡樂節日的精神已經燃起坎卜斯的憤怒，喚醒這一位古老的邪惡妖怪來懲罰不相信聖誕節的人們。當家喻戶曉的節慶主角化身成為惡魔開始攻擊這個破碎的家庭，迫使他們挺身為家人戰鬥，如果他們希望活下去....<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01105195966010c7ae5de3057f50b9362aa1847","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703108350d64bb59303f7b7c0be33fbeda67cce6","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bcb9d3240516afdac20403b8f67a45d2de90c5","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20aab2386449c82fbb2cbd05fa92c1fc1694d056","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8143e09556de60650a39cd8dde6e38707b7835bb","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391f0a9501d42867fc7e3803e234dfa8443b0711","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a90c2b47ad1d5da99458ca176acb78d390ef7f","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786b1d33d58005bad5f8767c8c961a47718bbaa7","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b2cde39d7a4a6ff4aef1a1de5c00ece175c177","tid":237564,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}